105
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:10,660
How pointless...

106
00:12:12,310 --> 00:12:16,040
I'll cut everything up into pieces!

107
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,800
Swordplay that cuts nothing...

108
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:26,360
Cut nothing... but cut steel... I don't
understand what it means at all!

109
00:12:27,900 --> 00:12:31,320
Thrust and Thrust... This is the
secret of powerful swordplay!

110
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:34,260
Atomic Spar!

111
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:38,410
I'll just cut you up!

112
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:09,370
