If you're not a swordsman...
then an excavator?!

119
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,110
I'm an assassin!

120
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:12,450
Sparks?! Just how fast is it spinning?!

121
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:16,040
They'll be repelled!

122
00:14:18,450 --> 00:14:23,840
