155
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:07,660
Listen. There're swordsmen out there
who are capable of cutting nothing.

156
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:15,190
Does "cutting nothing" mean...
know the rhythm...?

157
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:20,060
